  "last_modified_by": "LIU Dezhi (XC-CP/ESW2-CN)",
  "parent_id": "2411995729",
  "children": [],
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "该问题由Chery项目发现，copy一份在这里做汇总，最新版请参考chery原版，链接："
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "RTC RA8804CE unexpectedly triggered the AF flag"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "问题现象"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "JIRA问题链接： https://jira-shzj.auto-link.com.cn/browse/CHER-78745"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "【T1K国际】【中控】【电源管理】【实车】【客户问题】str30h后未自动关闭， 主机静态电流4.5mA左右（3/20）"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "复现操作"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": true,
      "items": [
        "客户实车连续两次测试30h从STR（4.5mA）退出进入深度休眠模式（0.5mA）失败，工作电流始终保持在4.5mA；",
        "故障件返回办公室后多次测试STR 5min，问题不复现；",
        "按照实际需求设置30h的STR用电脑抓DLT，最终复现问题；",
        "复现问题时，DLT记录到RTC返回的唤醒reason=5，如图1，该含义是TF=1&&AF=1，Fixed-Cycle Timer（TF: Timer Flag）和Alarm（AF： Alarm Flag）中断同时触发；",
        "分析LCM代码，发现对reason=5的判定，没有逻辑，导致了SCC LCM没有满足拉起SOC条件，直接走了SCC shut down，这也与客户问题现象吻合；",
        "另外，实际代码中用到的唤醒类型是Fixed-Cycle Timer，没有启用Alarm唤醒，这与期望不符；"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/19_RTC%20RA8804CE%20unexpectedly%20triggered%20the%20AF%20flag/image-2024-10-17_16-11-50.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/19_RTC RA8804CE unexpectedly triggered the AF flag/image-2024-10-17_16-11-50.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "图1"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "问题分析"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "针对上述步骤中5/6，得到了问题产生的根本原因有两个："
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "问题点1：LCM没有判断reason=5的情况？"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "目前看LCM代码对于reason=5没有做逻辑，当5的情况出现时，SCC无动作，直到SCC shut down，实际上需要把Fixed-Cycle Timer和Alarm中断标志同时置位后发给SOC作进一步判断，并拉起SOC，"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "如下图3，左边是修复前，右边修复后："
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/19_RTC%20RA8804CE%20unexpectedly%20triggered%20the%20AF%20flag/image-2024-10-10_10-10-26.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/19_RTC RA8804CE unexpectedly triggered the AF flag/image-2024-10-10_10-10-26.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "图3"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "问题点2：软件没有用Alarm中断，为何能读到AF标志？"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "图4是芯片厂家反馈的信息："
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/19_RTC%20RA8804CE%20unexpectedly%20triggered%20the%20AF%20flag/image-2024-10-10_10-16-8.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/19_RTC RA8804CE unexpectedly triggered the AF flag/image-2024-10-10_10-16-8.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "图4"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": true,
      "items": [
        "厂家反馈 图5 框图部分寄存器08~0A冷启动是随机数，因此当STR 30h内走时与随机数恰巧匹配，AF标志位会被置位，但因为AIE=0，没有产生中断；",
        "同时部分RTC芯片因为电容/工艺原因随机数不是真随机，会出现部分数值高概率出现的情况；",
        "第二点也是能够解释为什么客户反馈故障件能够高概率复现；",
        "目前随机数匹配导致的AF置位问题是唯一怀疑的可能原因，厂家也在针对这个芯片做上下电测试，读随机值分析；"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "ROOT CAUSE"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/19_RTC%20RA8804CE%20unexpectedly%20triggered%20the%20AF%20flag/image-2024-10-17_16-5-25.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/19_RTC RA8804CE unexpectedly triggered the AF flag/image-2024-10-17_16-5-25.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "图5"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/19_RTC%20RA8804CE%20unexpectedly%20triggered%20the%20AF%20flag/image-2024-10-17_17-38-29.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/19_RTC RA8804CE unexpectedly triggered the AF flag/image-2024-10-17_17-38-29.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "图6"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "16台机器上电读ALARM寄存器数据结果，如图5",
        "LCM逻辑判定错误，如图6；"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "解决方案"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/19_RTC%20RA8804CE%20unexpectedly%20triggered%20the%20AF%20flag/image-2024-10-17_17-42-10.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/19_RTC RA8804CE unexpectedly triggered the AF flag/image-2024-10-17_17-42-10.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "图7"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "修复方案如图7所示："
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "修复问题点1：增加LCM判断reason=5的情况"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "如图3所示修复，链接： https://rbcm-gerrit.de.bosch.com/q/topic:%22enter_str_fail_for_sop13%22"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "修复问题点2：RTC驱动：reason判定条件增加，冷启动初始化设置alarm为无效值"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": true,
      "items": [
        "冷启动上电时，RTC驱动设置寄存器08~0A数值为0，正常时间不会出现DAY/WEEK为0状况，因此alarm永远匹配不上，AF标志不会置位；",
        "reason判定条件更新："
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "RTC_WAKEUP_FIXED_CYCLE（4）：(TIE==1) && (TE==1) && (TF==1)",
        "RTC_WAKEUP_ALARM（3）：(AIE==1) &&(AF==1)",
        "RTC_WAKEUP_ALARM_AND_FIXED_CYCLE（5）：以上条件全部满足"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "修复链接： https://rbcm-gerrit.de.bosch.com/q/topic:%22enter_str_fail_for_sop13%22"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "结束"
    }
  ],
